ed="T" n="0791c15"/><anchor n="T.50.2061.0791c15"/><head><date from-iso="+0618-06-21" key="j19469512052491" to-iso="+0907-06-06">唐</date><placeName key="PL000000042229"><placeName>京師</placeName><placeName>崇聖寺</placeName></placeName><persName key="A002468">文綱</persName>傳（<persName key="A010786">名恪</persName>）</head><p><lb
ed="T" n="0791c16"/><persName key="A002468">釋文綱</persName>，姓<name>孔</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000013239">會稽</placeName>人也。曾祖<persName key="A010774">範</persName>，<placeName key="PL000000000074">陳</placeName>都官尚<lb
ed="T" n="0791c17"/>書；祖<persName key="A010775">禩</persName>，祠部侍郎；考<persName key="A019328">頂<anchor xml:id="beg0791sgsz4"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>坐</sic><corr>生</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0791sgsz4"/></persName>逃海避<placeName key="PL000000000105">隋</placeName>，擇木<ptr type="glossary" target="#g528"/><lb
ed="T" n="0791c18"/>歸<persName key="A002434">舜</persName>，<date from-iso="+0627-01-26" key="j19500921958296" to-iso="+0649-07-13"><name>貞觀</name></date>始拜尚乘直長；咸光復儒業，旁<lb
ed="T" n="0791c19"/>通釋教。是故<persName key="A002468">綱</persName>也植宿根，從習氣。慈母懷<lb
ed="T" n="0791c20"/>孕，雜食棄捐。有婆羅門<ptr rend="display:none;" type="glossary" target="#g117"/>僧頭陀語其母曰：<lb
ed="T" n="0791c21"/>「若此男，終紹三寶。」自爾每聞空中多異香、<lb
ed="T" n="0791c22"/>雜仙樂。及誕育之日，白鶴翔集，若臨視焉。<lb
ed="T" n="0791c23"/>比襁褓中，午後不受乳哺，猶堅持齋者。<anchor xml:id="beg0791sgsz5"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>重</sic><corr>童</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0791sgsz5"/><lb
ed="T" n="0791c24"/>齓，隨師訪道。<date key="j19573721957736" from-iso="+0647-01-01" to-iso="+0647-12-31">十二</date>出家，<date key="j19602941960658" from-iso="+0655-01-01" to-iso="+0655-12-31">冠年</date>受具。精慮苦<lb
ed="T" n="0791c25"/>行，專念息心，藜羹糗糧<ptr type="glossary" target="#g146"/>，麻衣草薦。操有彞檢，<lb
ed="T" n="0791c26"/>口無溢言。尋詣<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName>沙門<persName key="A008984">道成<roleName>律師</roleName></persName>，稟毘<lb
ed="T" n="0791c27"/>尼藏<ptr type="glossary" target="#g900"/>。<date key="j19621201962485" from-iso="+0660-01-01" to-iso="+0660-12-31">二十五</date>講律，<date key="j19639471964311" from-iso="+0665-01-01" to-iso="+0665-12-31">三十</date>登壇。每勤修深思，<lb
ed="T" n="0791c28"/>凝視反聽，淨如止水，嶷若斷山。或風雨宴<lb
ed="T" n="0791c29"/>居，或晝夜獨得。故能吉祥在手，不捨其瓶<ptr target="#n884"/>；<pb ed="T" n="0792a" xml:id="T50.2061.0792a"/><lb
ed="T" n="0792a01"/>威德<ptr type="glossary" target="#g148"/>迎風，不絕於氣。出籠瘠雁，坐致虛空，<lb
ed="T" n="0792a02"/>起屋下層，自然成就。<anchor xml:id="beg0792001"/>唯<anchor xml:id="end0792001"/>甘露之渧口，喻利<lb
ed="T" n="0792a03"/>劍之傷人，慎之，重之！廣矣，至矣！由是八<lb
ed="T" n="0792a04"/>方來學，《四分》永流，請益者舉袂雲臨，讚歎者<lb
ed="T" n="0792a05"/>發聲雷駭。<date notBefore-iso="+0700-05-31" key="j19768801977143" notAfter-iso="+0701-02-18"><name>久視</name>中</date>，天作淫雨<ptr target="#n887"/>，人有憂色。<persName key="A002468">綱</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0792a06"/><anchor xml:id="beg0792002"/>愍<anchor xml:id="end0792002"/>之，乃端坐思惟，却倚屋壁。奄至中夕，欻<lb
ed="T" n="0792a07"/>爾半傾，唯餘背間，嶷然山立，識者以為得神<lb
ed="T" n="0792a08"/>通，因定力故。日月靈跡，幽明潛感，兆於集<lb
ed="T" n="0792a09"/>事<ptr type="glossary" target="#g147"/>，應乎遣言。左右怪之，<persName key="A002468">綱</persName>曰：「夫真實無相，<lb
ed="T" n="0792a10"/>塵色本空。正覺<ptr type="glossary" target="#g26"/>圓常，大悲湛定，不可取也。」<lb
ed="T" n="0792a11"/>是以一時法主，<ref type="person" target="#A002099 #A002100 #A002461 #A000291">四朝帝</ref>師，同<persName key="A002188">迦葉</persName>之入城，<lb
ed="T" n="0792a12"/>遇<persName key="A005424">匿王</persName>之說戒，<placeName key="PL000000048271">竹園</placeName>門外別有沙彌，畢樹<ptr type="glossary" target="#g149"/><lb
ed="T" n="0792a13"/>枝間廣聞鵽鳥<ptr type="glossary" target="#g150"/><ptr target="#n885"/>。所以受潤者博，入見者深。<lb
ed="T" n="0792a14"/>萬病已痊，獲歡喜之藥；一心不染，解煩惱之<lb
ed="T" n="0792a15"/>繩。又恭承絲綸<ptr type="glossary" target="#g305"/>，<placeName key="PL000000042189">京都</placeName>翻譯<ptr target="#n888"/>，追論惠用，遠契<lb
ed="T" n="0792a16"/>如因，翹誠滿朝，檀施<ptr type="glossary" target="#g237"/>敵國，但依布薩<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1291"/>，盡用<lb
ed="T" n="0792a17"/>莊嚴<ptr type="glossary" target="#g319"/>。累歷伽藍二十餘所，凡是塔廟，各已華<lb
ed="T" n="0792a18"/>豐。猶且刺血書經，向六百卷；登壇受具，僅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g175"/><lb
ed="T" n="0792a19"/>數千人。至苦至勤，納無我<ptr type="glossary" target="#g627"/>之海；不寢不食，<lb
ed="T" n="0792a20"/>種無生<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1368"/>之田。<date from-iso="+0704-02-14" key="j19782341978588" to-iso="+0705-02-02"><name>長安</name>四年</date>，奉勅往<anchor xml:id="beg0792sgsz1"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0792sgsz1"/>州<placeName key="PL000000042886">無憂王<lb
ed="T" n="0792a21"/>寺</placeName>迎舍利<ptr target="#n885"/>。<date from-iso="+0708-02-01" key="j19796821980065" to-iso="+0709-02-18"><name>景龍</name>二載</date>，<persName key="A002100">中宗孝和皇帝</persName>延入內<lb
ed="T" n="0792a22"/>道場行道，送真身舍利往<placeName key="PL000000042886">無憂王寺</placeName>入塔。<lb
ed="T" n="0792a23"/><date from-iso="+0708-02-01" key="j19796821980065" to-iso="+0709-02-18">其年</date>於<placeName key="PL000000057329">乾陵宮</placeName>為內尼受戒。復於宮中坐<lb
ed="T" n="0792a24"/>夏<ptr target="#n889"/>，為<ref type="person" target="#A002146 #A002461">二聖</ref>內尼講《四分律》一遍。<persName key="A002100">中宗</persName>嘉尚，<lb
ed="T" n="0792a25"/>為度弟子，賜什物、綵帛三千匹。因奏道場<lb
ed="T" n="0792a26"/>靈感之事，<date key="j19798351979835" when-iso="+0708-07-03">六月七日</date>，御札題牓為<placeName key="PL000000057408">靈感寺</placeName>是<lb
ed="T" n="0792a27"/>也，諸寺辟碩德以隷焉。夫其左<placeName key="PL000000042089">籞宿</placeName>，右<placeName key="PL000000057409">上<lb
ed="T" n="0792a28"/>林</placeName>，南臺<placeName key="PL000000042627">終山</placeName>，北池<placeName key="PL000000042014">渭水</placeName>。千門宮闕，化出雲<lb
ed="T" n="0792a29"/>霄，萬乘旌旗，天迴原隰<ptr type="glossary" target="#g158"/>。<date from-iso="+0712-09-16" key="j19813711981836" to-iso="+0713-12-25"><name>先天</name>載</date><persName key="A002461">睿宗聖真皇<pb ed="T" n="0792b" xml:id="T50.2061.0792b"/><lb
ed="T" n="0792b01"/>帝</persName>，又於別殿請為菩薩戒師<ptr target="#n892"/>，妃主環階，侍從<lb
ed="T" n="0792b02"/>羅拜。<placeName key="PL000000055446">兜率天</placeName>上，親聽法言；<placeName key="PL000000048261">王舍城</placeName>中，普聞淨<lb
ed="T" n="0792b03"/>戒。恩旨賜絹三千餘匹，<persName key="A002468">綱</persName>悉付常住<ptr type="glossary" target="#g151"/>，隨事<lb
ed="T" n="0792b04"/>修營。或金地繚垣，用增上價；或寶坊飛閣，<lb
ed="T" n="0792b05"/>克壯全模；或講堂經樓，舍利淨土；或軒廊器<lb
ed="T" n="0792b06"/>物，厨庫園林，皆信施法財，周給僧寶。方將<lb
ed="T" n="0792b07"/>示迷津，引覺路，濯熱火宅<ptr type="glossary" target="#g1598"/>，拯溺毒流，而乃<lb
ed="T" n="0792b08"/>奄忽<ptr type="glossary" target="#g153"/>神遷，斯須薪盡<ptr type="glossary" target="#g152"/>，雖有應化，何其速歟！<lb
ed="T" n="0792b09"/>以<date key="j19868421986842" when-iso="+0727-09-09"><name>開元</name>十五年八月十五日</date>怡然長往，時春<lb
ed="T" n="0792b10"/>秋九十有二<ptr target="#n893"/>。<date key="j19868601986860" when-iso="+0727-09-27">其年九月四日</date>，塔<anchor xml:id="beg0792sgsz2"/>於<anchor xml:id="end0792sgsz2"/>寺側焉。聞<lb
ed="T" n="0792b11"/>哀奔喪，執紼<ptr type="glossary" target="#g504"/>會葬，香<anchor xml:id="beg0792sgsz3"/>華<anchor xml:id="end0792sgsz3"/><anchor xml:id="begd1e22880"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>憧</sic><corr>幢</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="endd1e22880"/>蓋，緇素華夷，填<lb
ed="T" n="0792b12"/>城塞川，篲雲翳景，蓋數萬人。有若法侶，<placeName key="PL000000042192">京<lb
ed="T" n="0792b13"/>兆</placeName><persName key="A001899">懷素</persName>、<persName key="A010776">滿意</persName>、<persName key="A009082">承禮</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000027118">襄陽</placeName><persName key="A010777">崇拔</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042848">扶風</placeName><persName key="A010778">鳳林</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000027770">江陵</placeName><persName key="A008970">恒<lb
ed="T" n="0792b14"/>景</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000020588">淄川</placeName><persName key="A010786">名恪</persName>等百餘人，咸曰：「智河舟遷，法宇<lb
ed="T" n="0792b15"/>棟橈而已哉！」有若弟子，<placeName key="PL000000010783">淮南</placeName><persName key="A008876">道岸</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000035107">蜀川</placeName><persName key="A010779">神積</persName>、<lb
ed="T" n="0792b16"/><placeName key="PL000000042848"><anchor xml:id="beg0792sgsz4"/>岐<anchor xml:id="end0792sgsz4"/></placeName><placeName key="PL000000042949">隴</placeName><persName key="A010780">慧顗</persName>、<placeName key="PL000000042192">京兆</placeName><persName key="A010781">神慧</persName>、<persName key="A010782">思義</persName>、<persName key="A010783">紹覺</persName>、<persName key="A023223">律藏</persName>、<persName key="A010784">恒暹</persName>、<persName key="A010785">崇業</persName><lb
ed="T" n="0792b17"/>等五十餘人，並目以慈眼入於度門，金棺<ptr target="#n899"/><lb
ed="T" n="0792b18"/>不追<ptr type="glossary" target="#g154"/>，灰骨罔答。乃請<placeName key="PL000000024155">滑臺</placeName>太守<persName key="A007761">李邕</persName>為碑。<lb
ed="T" n="0792b19"/><persName key="A007761">邕</persName>象彼<persName key="A004022">馬遷</persName>，法其<persName key="A008642"><anchor xml:id="beg0792003"/>班<anchor xml:id="end0792003"/><roleName>氏</roleName></persName>，以二人而同傳，<lb
ed="T" n="0792b20"/>必百行以齊肩。不忝<persName key="A001899">懷素</persName>前，不慚<persName key="A001519">宣<roleName>師</roleName></persName><lb
ed="T" n="0792b21"/>後，<persName key="A007761">李北海</persName>題品<ptr type="glossary" target="#g156"/>，不其韙<ptr type="glossary" target="#g155"/>乎！有<placeName key="PL000000020588">淄州</placeName><persName key="A010786">名恪<roleName>律<lb
ed="T" n="0792b22"/>師</roleName></persName>者，精執律範，切勤求解，嘗廁<persName key="A001519">宣<roleName>師</roleName></persName>法筵，<lb
ed="T" n="0792b23"/>躬問《鈔序》<ptr target="#n900"/>義。<persName key="A001519">宣<roleName>師</roleName></persName>親錄，隨喜靈感壇，班名<lb
ed="T" n="0792b24"/><anchor xml:id="begd1e22921"/>於<anchor xml:id="endd1e22921"/>經末<ptr target="#n901"/>，又附麗<ptr type="glossary" target="#g157"/><persName key="A002468">文綱</persName>之門也。</p>
